====================================
wordpress-cl    - post from your CLI
====================================

Simple posting program using python-wordpress-xmlrpc

You can get python-wordpress-xmlrpc from here:
https://github.com/maxcutler/python-wordpress-xmlrpc

Execute it this way to create a default config.wp (you will need configobj module)
python config.py

Just configure it (username and password and url of course!)
and use it this way:
chmod +x wordpress-cl.py
mv wordpress-cl.py wordpress-cl
wordpress-cl title postFile.html

Very useful (at least for me)
